item.title: CVE-2017-16038|2024-09-16T19:19:36.920Z -- hackerone -- f2e-server%20node%20module
item.description: `f2e-server` 1.12.11 and earlier is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url. This is compounded by `f2e-server` requiring elevated privileges to run.
